    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You place a seal on the ground. The seal then conceals itself and is invisible to all creatures without chakra sight. <br />  <em><strong>Activation:</strong></em> As a bonus action on subsequent turns, you can trigger this seal's activation. When activated the seal releases a massive gust of force sending anything within range flying upward. Creatures within a 10 foot radius of the seal must make a Strength saving throw, taking 2d6 Force damage and being lifted 10 feet in the air on a failed save. Targets lifted by this jutsu remain that way until the end of the start of your next turn. After this effect has been triggered the jutsu ends.</p><p>Alternatively, this jutsu can deal no damage and instead lift willing creatures up to 30 feet in the air, but you must declare this during the casting of this jutsu.</p>",
